      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3222_1",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "1、量筒的使用：液体物质的体积可以用量筒测出。量筒（量杯）的使用方法：",
        "bbox": [
          0.04575034509958588,
          0.10300748384697625,
          0.7326628541379083,
          0.12085715613814903
        ],
        "order": 2
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3222_2",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "①观察量筒标度的单位。1L=1dm1mL=1cm{",
        "bbox": [
          0.046276211135213303,
          0.14382001580439735,
          0.4246368237691448,
          0.16176265513875332
        ],
        "order": 3
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3222_3",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "②观察量筒的最大测量值（量程）和分度值（最小刻度）。",
        "bbox": [
          0.046144744626306446,
          0.1850973829777344,
          0.5618878590679025,
          0.2026681541393576
        ],
        "order": 4
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3222_4",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "③读数时，视线与量筒中凹液面的底部相平（或与量筒中凸液面的顶部相平）。",
        "bbox": [
          0.04680207717084073,
          0.22628178310788824,
          0.7422599092881088,
          0.24366662018314508
        ],
        "order": 5
      },
      {
        "id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_3222_5",
        "observed_type": "text",
        "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
        "text": "2、测量液体和固体的密度：只要测量出物质的质量和体积，通过ρ=m/V就能够算出物质的密度。质量 可以用天平测出，液体和形状不规则的固体的体积可以用量筒或量杯来测量。",
        "bbox": [
          0.046276211135213303,
          0.26737321619485893,
          0.9515545914678236,
          0.30363036303630364
        ],
        "order": 6
      }
    ]
